Package: rkainu
Title: Finnish Spirometry and DLCO Reference Values (Kainu et al. 2015, 2017)
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Rikhard", "Mäki-Heikkilä", , "rikhard.maki-heikkila@tuni.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predicted values, z-scores, lower limits of normal (LLN), and
    percent-predicted for Finnish adult spirometry (Kainu et al. 2015) and
    diffusing capacity (DLCO; Kainu et al. 2017). Spirometry covers FVC, FEV1,
    FEV1/FVC, FEV6, FEV1/FEV6, PEF, MMEF, MEF75, MEF50, and MEF25 for adults
    aged 18-90. DLCO covers DLCOc, DLCOc/VA (KCO), and VA. The spirometry API
    mirrors 'rspiro' for easy side-by-side comparison with GLI-2012 values.
